        "content": "import geopandas as gpd\n\ngdf = arg\n\nfiltered_gdf = gdf.set_crs(32632)\nfiltered_gdf = filtered_gdf.to_crs(3395)\n\nfiltered_gdf = filtered_gdf[filtered_gdf['mean']>0]\n\n# Use __dict__ to bypass pandas' \"new attribute\" UserWarning on sliced\n# DataFrames; curio reads .metadata back via getattr (parsers.py).\nfiltered_gdf.__dict__['metadata'] = {\n   'name': 'census'\n}\n\nreturn filtered_gdf",
